Begin forwarded message: 
From: Benjamin Goggin
Date: July 9, 2019 at 7:20:41 PM EDT 
To: 
Subject: Business Insider, Request for comment 
Hi 
My name is Ben Goggin, Pm writing a story for Business Insider about your participation in the rosecution of 
Jeffrey Epstein and wanted to ask you a few questions. I'll list them here but feel free to call me 
*can you confirm that you are 30 years old? 
*can you respond to criticisms that you have a conflict of interest due to your father, your past political 
donations, or your reported attendence of the women's march? Is the picture on this blog you? 
*can you comment on your work at Debevoise & Plimpton LLP? 
*can you elaborate on what happened in the 2016 case against the camp counselor who allegedly solicited nude 
photos from a middle schooler? Why did he plead to a lesser charge? 
Thank you! 
Best, 
Benjamin Goggin 
Weekend Editor
